üîπ 1. Show all orders with customer names
Query:
SELECT O.OrderID, C.CustomerName, O.OrderDate
FROM Orders O
JOIN Customers C ON O.CustomerID = C.CustomerID;

Output:
OrderIDCustomerNameOrderDate1Ravi Kumar2025-10-012Sneha Sharma2025-10-033John Doe2025-10-054Ravi Kumar2025-10-06

üîπ 2. Total sales amount per order
Query:
SELECT 
    OD.OrderID,
    SUM(P.Price * OD.Quantity) AS TotalAmount
FROM OrderDetails OD
JOIN Products P ON OD.ProductID = P.ProductID
GROUP BY OD.OrderID;

Output:
OrderIDTotalAmount169,000.00225,000.0037,000.00427,000.00
üí° Explanation:
Order 1 ‚Üí 1 Laptop (‚Çπ65,000) + 2 Headphones (‚Çπ2,000√ó2) = ‚Çπ69,000
Order 4 ‚Üí 1 Mobile (‚Çπ25,000) + 1 Headphone (‚Çπ2,000) = ‚Çπ27,000

üîπ 3. Total revenue by product category
Query:
SELECT 
    P.Category,
    SUM(P.Price * OD.Quantity) AS TotalRevenue
FROM OrderDetails OD
JOIN Products P ON OD.ProductID = P.ProductID
GROUP BY P.Category;

Output:
CategoryTotalRevenueElectronics115,000.00Accessories6,000.00Fashion7,000.00

üîπ 4. Top 3 customers by total spending
Query:
SELECT 
    C.CustomerName,
    SUM(P.Price * OD.Quantity) AS TotalSpent
FROM Customers C
JOIN Orders O ON C.CustomerID = O.CustomerID
JOIN OrderDetails OD ON O.OrderID = OD.OrderID
JOIN Products P ON OD.ProductID = P.ProductID
GROUP BY C.CustomerName
ORDER BY TotalSpent DESC
LIMIT 3;

Output:
CustomerNameTotalSpentRavi Kumar96,000.00Sneha Sharma25,000.00John Doe7,000.00

üîπ 5. Most popular product (by quantity sold)
Query:
SELECT 
    P.ProductName,
    SUM(OD.Quantity) AS TotalSold
FROM OrderDetails OD
JOIN Products P ON OD.ProductID = P.ProductID
GROUP BY P.ProductName
ORDER BY TotalSold DESC
LIMIT 1;

Output:
ProductNameTotalSoldHeadphones3
üí° Explanation:
Headphones sold 3 units across multiple orders ‚Üí most popular product.

üîπ 6. Monthly sales trend
Query:
SELECT 
    DATE_FORMAT(O.OrderDate, '%Y-%m') AS Month,
    SUM(P.Price * OD.Quantity) AS MonthlySales
FROM Orders O
JOIN OrderDetails OD ON O.OrderID = OD.OrderID
JOIN Products P ON OD.ProductID = P.ProductID
GROUP BY Month
ORDER BY Month;

Output:
MonthMonthlySales2025-10128,000.00
üí° Explanation:
All orders occurred in October 2025, so total monthly sales = ‚Çπ128,000.

üß† Final Insights:


Top Customer: Ravi Kumar


Best-Selling Product: Headphones


Most Profitable Category: Electronics


Total Revenue (October 2025): ‚Çπ128,000



